{"tid":1788441,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳鉅源出獄後兩度旋即斥1.85億買新地樓","createTime":"2019-12-18T16:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T17:58:31.000Z","uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"27bf7af152c89ba834dff755a0809896489d2fbe","tid":1788441,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"在郭炳江本月出獄前夕，被郭老太視為第四個仔、因新地（016）賄賂案被判入獄的新地前執董陳鉅源及配偶，兩度掃入新地樓。陳鉅源去年因血癌惡化，被赦免提早兩個月出獄。身為新地前重臣，養病期間亦不忘掃樓，出獄兩月已旋即斥1.85億元掃入兩個由新地發展的豪宅天鑄單位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789528e66fa91da5e1d2e04d5a5247b3bfc2ab27","tid":1788441,"uid":124983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"原定於2018年12月19日出獄，但在獄中發現患上血癌，病情惡化，醫生認為不宜繼續在監獄醫院留醫，懲教署長因此向特首匯報，同年10月中獲特首<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">赦免</span></span>餘下刑期出獄治療。<br />\n<br />\n法治有險可守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5400811ab8c8bda1c7d5c0c8d1211b62786f9f2","tid":1788441,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2914648b44cdc4f6d08db560f898e5e4e0629876","tid":1788441,"uid":149266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"死咗 咁層樓會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf988fb24bdadf85da933c307c6047daf60cffbf","tid":1788441,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789528e66fa91da5e1d2e04d5a5247b3bfc2ab27","tid":1788441,"uid":124983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"原定於2018年12月19日出獄，但在獄中發現患上血癌，病情惡化，醫生認為不宜繼續在監獄醫院留醫，懲教署長因此向特首匯報，同年10月中獲特首<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">赦免</span></span>餘下刑期出獄治療。<br />\n<br />\n法治有險可守<